- **Drag & Drop**: Handle `Drop` on the chat area to detect `.png/.jpg/.jpeg/.bmp` files and set `AttachedImagePath`.
- **Clipboard paste**: Handle `Ctrl+V` in the text box — if clipboard contains an image, save it to a temp file and set `AttachedImagePath`.

